# How to restore your password

If you forget your password, you can request to restore your password via email.

1. On the Sign in page, click **[Forgot your password?](https://my.b2bdemo.net/en/restore)** ![Sign in page!](https://4.downloader.disk.yandex.ru/preview/c3fabb41ca12102947749ef8a94dc1b247117938a3cc3dff8fdc71c8f94eea86/inf/vKr225PjWapHZy-0cAMjevWEo14WYisRvNHNLA1cM190zxMnbgGzRlxwnmpbpacunDFZN9JtqymdslMghq2zmw%3D%3D?uid=19802370&filename=sign_in_page.jpg&disposition=inline&hash=&limit=0&content_type=image%2Fjpeg&owner_uid=19802370&tknv=v2&size=1024x512)
2. Enter your **email address** to find your account, then click **Send**. ![Password restore page!](https://3.downloader.disk.yandex.ru/preview/6284611bd745ef0b7830956ba331962d59807fa350fb79a289678507c0cef0bf/inf/toZicC-kluny-RyT_APWYPUhHL9vZFZSmHESpxEZDZ_KsUSzg9LrLoEeZUWvn5F3f83sVJ2-MelQeGB_wK9TFA%3D%3D?uid=19802370&filename=restore_a_password.jpg&disposition=inline&hash=&limit=0&content_type=image%2Fjpeg&owner_uid=19802370&tknv=v2&size=1024x512)
3. Check your email inbox. B2Brocker will send a message to your email address immediately.
4. From the email, click **a link to get back into your account**.
5. When prompted, **choose a new password**.
